OL,3,CRural fire stations could be saved by
OL,4,C#1.8m from government
OL,6,FFire stations in Dorset and Wiltshire
OL,7,Fthat were at risk of closure look set
OL,8,Fto be saved thanks to a #1.8million
OL,9,Fgovernment grant.
OL,11,FIn February, Dorset and Wiltshire Fire
OL,12,FAuthority proposed closing stations in
OL,13,FBradford-on-Avon, Charmouth,
OL,14,FCranborne, Hamworthy, Maiden Newton,
OL,15,FMere, Ramsbury and Wilton.
OL,17,FIt said it was necessary to address a
OL,18,Ffunding gap of more than #1.2million.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
