OL,3,CRural fire stations could be saved by
OL,4,C#1.8m from government
OL,6,FFollowing local opposition, chief fire
OL,7,Fofficer Andy Cole suggested saving
OL,8,Ffour of the stations for at least a
OL,9,Fyear, with the other four stations to
OL,10,Fmerge and become two.
OL,12,FNow, all eight stations may be able to
OL,13,Fstay open due to a one-off government
OL,14,Fgrant.
OL,16,FHowever, that depends on the Fire
OL,17,FAuthority being allowed to raise more
OL,18,Ffrom council tax.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1782042480
OL,3,CRural fire stations could be saved by
OL,4,C#1.8m from government
OL,6,FMr Cole said: "I've been looking at
OL,7,Fevery opportunity available to improve
OL,8,Fthe Service's financial position and
OL,9,Fremove the need for station closures
OL,10,Fand job losses.
OL,12,F"One of those opportunities was a bid
OL,13,Fto Government for funding to support
OL,14,Fwork we have been doing around
OL,15,Finnovation, data, technology and
OL,16,Fservice improvement.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1782042480
OL,3,CRural fire stations could be saved by
OL,4,C#1.8m from government
OL,6,F"I am really pleased that this has
OL,7,Fbeen successful and secured the
OL,8,FService #1.8million of one-off
OL,9,FGovernment funding, which we will
OL,10,Freceive imminently."
OL,12,FMr Cole added that the government
OL,13,Fgrant would only be a temporary fix.
OL,15,FHe said: "This one-off funding does
OL,16,Fnot resolve the Authority's long-term
OL,17,Ffinancial position and we continue to
OL,18,Fface a deficit in future years,
OL,19,Fhowever it does provide more time for
OL,20,Fthe Service to make changes through
OL,21,Four modernisation programme."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
