OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1782042480
OL,3,CRural fire stations could be saved by
OL,4,C#1.8m from government
OL,6,FHis advice is that all eight stations
OL,7,Fstay open, as long as they are
OL,8,Fmodernised. The Fire Authority will
OL,9,Fmake its decision on 30 June.
OL,11,FMr Cole said the stations would only
OL,12,Fsurvive long-term if the authority was
OL,13,F"granted flexibility to raise council
OL,14,Ftax precept to at least the national
OL,15,Faverage for fire services for 2027/28".
OL,17,FThe Fire Authority needs permission
OL,18,Ffrom the government to raise its
OL,19,Fcouncil tax precept. If allowed, it
OL,20,Fwill make a decision on how much this
OL,21,Fwill be in February 2027.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1782042480
OL,3,CRural fire stations could be saved by
OL,4,C#1.8m from government
OL,6,FMr Cole added that if the council tax
OL,7,Fprecept didn't increase, or there were
OL,8,Fmore funding cuts, he would advise the
OL,9,FFire Authority to close all eight fire
OL,10,Fstations.
OL,12,FThe next step is for Fire Authority
OL,13,FMembers to vote on Mr Cole's
OL,14,Frecommendations on the 30 June.
OL,16,FMr Cole said they would then continue
OL,17,Fto lobby government for the fire
OL,18,Fprecept flexibility - which will be
OL,19,Fconfirmed in February 2027.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
